{"tid":1352813,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【7月27日】一齊行出嚟，其實黑社會又有乜好怕","createTime":"2019-07-23T00:19:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T21:55:58.000Z","uid":273854,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b13e8dc43bdf699f21cb4db8061afab00df38c4a","tid":1352813,"uid":273854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T00:19:00.000Z","msg":"唔好再中tvb或者古惑仔毒<br />\n黑社會其實同大陸人一樣<br />\n大部份都係膽小如鼠<br />\n人多就惡<br />\n人少就死狗<br />\n<br />\n1. 點解要入黑社會?<br />\n因為要威?<br />\n無論, 係要威, 但入黑社會嘅大部份人<br />\n都係本身無料嘅人<br />\n知道自己一個人冇能力去威<br />\n先要加入社團，依靠人多去作威作福<br />\n<br />\n2. 黑社會好勇武?<br />\n係, 黑社會比良好市民更加唔怕犯事<br />\n但唔係因為佢地天生勇武<br />\n只係佢地唔會有案底包袱<br />\n你地嗰一班前線，絕對比佢地勇武<br />\n<br />\n3. 黑社會有冇惡人?<br />\n有<br />\n但呢個年代全部都好低調<br />\n因為高調又惡嗰班<br />\n97 嗰期已經比黑白兩邊搞掂晒<br />\n<br />\n4. 真人真事<br />\n唔講牛屎黑呢啲低層次生物<br />\n就算以前尖咀嗰班大佬<br />\n比警察拉左返去<br />\n都只係喺班靚面前屌鬼<br />\n剩返一個時即死狗&quot; 阿sir,  係班細嘅面前比返少少面丫&quot;。<br />\n<br />\n5. 點先叫惡?<br />\n人多<br />\n下面條片雖然係電影<br />\n但絕對係人多就惡嘅寫照<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=7iXJuJTL528\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D7iXJuJTL528&d=4HHrVRRB2qdXUamIokVXjUPclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=4ec0dbaf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=7iXJuJTL528</a><br />\n<br />\n6. 要唔要小心?<br />\n要<br />\n因為牛屎黑有個特點<br />\n就係易失控<br />\n但當佢地見到惡唔起時<br />\n就會走住黎屌<br />\n(牛佬)<br />\n<br />\n7. 星期六仲會唔會有牛黑有組織咁出黎搞事?<br />\n呢排有好多fake rumors<br />\n但有一個係應該係真<br />\n就係背後搞手本身只想target 示威人士<br />\n但去到後期班牛黑 (第6 點)失晒控<br />\n搞到政府爆晒鑊 (唔好信嗰啲陰謀論唔該)<br />\n短期內,政府應該都唔會比呢班牛黑再出黎<br />\n(我琴日已經屌左鬼, 叫大家唔好不停post 嗰啲吹雞fake rumors) <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">8. 大家唔好再自己嚇自己<br />\n星期六, 7 月27 日<br />\n我地一齊出黎<br />\n捉拿犯人!!!<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"589bbfa915b8ab9a80adde77452af3f51fc5ca9e","tid":1352813,"uid":267969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T00:19:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8463d5187ee8e8854d16d61bbc6eb88efc45d660","tid":1352813,"uid":276365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T00:23:06.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"10e0acbdb8bdfcecfcd33a881b3e3c36849b5c55","tid":1352813,"uid":267969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T00:24:44.000Z","msg":"唔好向懼怕屈服<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"c738f6ad50324817066fda39e7e8fc0b7fb2c32c","tid":1352813,"uid":13119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T00:31:47.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n求下大家 一齊出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abc6ae30506ba1ab3856558e31d25d94077ea9be","tid":1352813,"uid":76368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T00:35:26.000Z","msg":"唔好向懼怕屈服, 7月27日一齊行出嚟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"472b9c85bb0002f2851c7d78d05cc59d9f3eb267","tid":1352813,"uid":115660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T00:35:41.000Z","msg":"香港人終於連黑社會都唔驚<br />\n<br />\n總之 打佢老母"},{"pid":"cff3242f80b5794ff960c53aad1200210f5c8c74","tid":1352813,"uid":273854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:02:04.000Z","msg":"推呀<br />\n唔好再比啲危言聳聽嘅post 嚇到大家唔敢出黎<br />\n<br />\n我琴日出左個post ,話各區白衣人吹雞係流料<br />\n已經即刻有負評<br />\n<br />\n小心對家玩分化<br />\n玩嚇鬼!!!"},{"pid":"b3f7461a5edc2148655644d8d27d4503a8870eb5","tid":1352813,"uid":57328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:06:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/Y8UyEFx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY8UyEFx.png&h=d3096026&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n元朗勢力分佈圖，有唔明隨時回答"},{"pid":"0121796d8cb0624b73d895cc720e2b1b012419dd","tid":1352813,"uid":211525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b3f7461a5edc2148655644d8d27d4503a8870eb5","tid":1352813,"uid":57328,"like":0,"dislike":0,